items.title: 5 climbers, including dad and teen daughter, killed by avalanche
items.description: Two men and a woman were recovered dead on Saturday, while the bodies of a man and his 17-year-old daughter were found on Sunday.

items.title: Hamas returns 3 more Israeli hostages' remains, leaving 8 still in Gaza
items.description: Among the 8 deceased Israeli hostages whose remains are yet to be returned from Gaza is soldier and U.S. citizen Itay Chen.

items.title: At least 20 people killed as powerful quake hits northern Afghanistan
items.description: Afghanistan's Taliban government says a powerful earthquake in the country's north has killed at least 20 people and left hundreds injured.
